- ‚úÖ **Code Analysis**
    - analyze_imports
    - analyze_file
    - find_references

- ‚ö†Ô∏èüîÑ **File Operations** (Always backup before use)
    - file_operations
    - version_control (Creates dated backups)
    - 
- ‚ö†Ô∏èüîÑ **Code Modify** (Always backup before use)
  - code_modifier (Performs modifying code line by line)(Currently has big issues) 
  
### Testing Phase
- üîÑ check_syntax
